title: Apple Faces Potential Watch Import Ban After Federal Trade Ruling
description: The tech giant can petition the Biden administration or look to other options after a ruling it violated patents related to blood-oxygen sensor.

title: Amazon's Profit Triples as Sales Show Resilience

title: X's Tumultuous First Year Under Elon Musk, in Charts
